1467
01:18:06.292 --> 01:18:08.583
I want to know what
actually happened that night.

1468
01:18:17.875 --> 01:18:19.208
-Maheshwari. are youГўв‚¬В¦
-[gasps]

1469
01:18:20.208 --> 01:18:21.083
